'''三牌楼站'''，位于今[[南京市|南京市]][[三牌楼大街|三牌楼大街]]北侧，是[[宁省铁路|宁省铁路]]的车站。1909年通车，有2条站线，1958年被拆除<ref name=njjtz>{{Cite book|title=南京交通志|url=https://books.google.com/books/about/%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%BF%97.html?id=2W9FAQAACAAJ|publisher=海天出版社|date=1994|language=zh}}</ref>。本站距[[下关站|下关站]]3.6公里，距[[丁家桥站|丁家桥站]]1.3公里<ref>{{Cite book|title=南京公用事业志|url=https://books.google.com/books?hl=zh-CN&id=HdNhAAAAIAAJ&dq=%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E5%BF%97|publisher=海天出版社|date=1994|isbn=978-7-80615-111-2|language=zh|access-date=2022-01-04|archive-date=2022-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220104060518/https://books.google.com/books?hl=zh-CN&id=HdNhAAAAIAAJ&dq=%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E5%BF%97}}</ref>。

